    {
      "id": "PopularPost322350",
      "post_content": "This is terrible for Exalted. Remember, Exalted creatures give the bonus to themselves. That means that [Knight of Glory](/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Knight of Glory), attacking alone, is a 3/2 -- already better than this guy attacking alone -- *and* it's in a more useful color *and* it has protection from black *and* you have the option of attacking with something else instead and still having it give its bonus to them.  \n  \nThis card is simply terrible; Exalted decks have strictly-better options.",
      "posted_by": "Aquillion",
      "html": "<div class=\"post oddItem\" id=\"PopularPost322350\">\n<span class=\"postContent\" id=\"ctl00_ctl00_ctl00_MainContent_SubContent_SubContent_popularPosts_postsRepeater_ctl05_post\">This is terrible for Exalted.  Remember, Exalted creatures give the bonus to themselves.  That means that <a class=\"autoCard\" data:cardname=\"Knight of Glory\" href=\"/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Knight of Glory\">Knight of Glory</a>, attacking alone, is a 3/2 -- already better than this guy attacking alone -- <i>and</i> it's in a more useful color <i>and</i> it has protection from black <i>and</i> you have the option of attacking with something else instead and still having it give its bonus to them.<br/><br/>This card is simply terrible; Exalted decks have strictly-better options.</span>\n<div class=\"postDetails\" id=\"ctl00_ctl00_ctl00_MainContent_SubContent_SubContent_popularPosts_postsRepeater_ctl05_postDetails\" style=\"padding-top: 5px;\">\n<div class=\"reportAbuse\">\n<a href=\"http://wizards.custhelp.com/cgi-bin/wizards.cfg/php/enduser/ask.php?p_prods=522,706,739&amp;p_cats=\" id=\"ctl00_ctl00_ctl00_MainContent_SubContent_SubContent_popularPosts_postsRepeater_ctl05_reportAbuseLink\" onclick=\"HandleReportPost(this, '322350'); return false;\">\r\n                                    Report Abuse</a>\u00a0\u00a0\r\n                                \r\n                            </div>\n<div class=\"postedBy\">\r\n                                Posted By: \r\n                                <span id=\"PostedBy93120\">Aquillion</span>\r\n                                (6/15/2013 1:24:12 AM)\r\n                            </div>\n<div class=\"postRating\">\n<div class=\"postRatingLabel\">\r\n                                    Rating:\u00a0\r\n                                </div>\n<div style=\"float: left;\">\n<div class=\"starRating\" id=\"ctl00_ctl00_ctl00_MainContent_SubContent_SubContent_popularPosts_postsRepeater_ctl05_postRating_starRating\"><img alt=\"0.5\"